      <p><a href="ch77s12.html#PsionicMonsters128">Elans</a> typically stand just under 6 feet tall and weigh in the neighborhood of 180 pounds, with men sometimes taller and heavier than women, but not always.</p>
      <p><a href="ch77s12.html#PsionicMonsters128">Elans</a> speak Common.</p>
      <p>Most <a href="ch77s12.html#PsionicMonsters128">elans</a> are psions or psychic warriors.</p>
