          <a class="indexterm" name="PsionicMonsters130"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Repletion (Su):</strong></span> By expending 1 power point, an <a href="ch77s12.html#PsionicMonsters128">elan</a> does not need to eat or drink for 24 hours.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2477407"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="PsionicMonsters131"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Resilience (Su):</strong></span> As an immediate action, an <a href="ch77s12.html#PsionicMonsters128">elan</a> can reduce the damage he is about to take by 2 points for every 1 power point spent.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2477447"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="PsionicMonsters132"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Resistance (Su):</strong></span> As an immediate action, an élan can spent 1 power point to gain a +4 racial bonus on saving throws until the beginning of his next turn.</p>
          <p>The <a href="ch77s12.html#PsionicMonsters128">elan</a> warrior presented here had the following ability scores before racial adjustments: Str 13, Dex 11, Con 12, Int 10, Wis 9, Cha 8.</p>
        </div>
